    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Well, for this functionality we currently rely entirely on numpy -- so this is also an issue there.\n\nIn any case, the operation you're looking for is `np.logical_not`, which should work fine on pandas objects. I tend to prefer `logical_not` to `~` for exactly these sorts of reasons.\n"
